{"tid":1076877,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【東華】傳媒報導 副校長 欺凌 事件 連夜發聲明","createTime":"2019-03-25T07:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T14:09:30.000Z","uid":1014,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9dd9751a63dbfbc85b91b0c6b57d606e9c66ede0","tid":1076877,"uid":1014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:25:46.000Z","msg":"聲明一：(星期六 10:15pm)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1075194/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1075194/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n聲明二：(星期日接近午夜)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/108662814816/posts/10157081024774817?sfns=xmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F108662814816%2Fposts%2F10157081024774817%3Fsfns%3Dxmo&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6d%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=a289c418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/108662814816/posts/10157081024774817?sfns=xmo</a><br />\n<br />\n聲明<br />\n<br />\n就有公眾人物在其社交媒體評論本院辛亥年總理中學副校長及老師一事，東華三院嚴正聲明其內容並無事實根據，且評論亦欠公允、客觀及證據。本院於三月二十三日所發出的聲明中，已闡述該校有關教務管理措施，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">在經本院檢視後證實並未有無理的安排</span></span>。本院重申如有遇到不公平對待的老師，可向本院直接反映。<br />\n<br />\n就有外界人士對本院教職人員作出<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不公正及欠實據</span></span>的評論，本院深表極度遺憾及促請有關人士<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">從速撤回</span></span>有關評論，以正視聽。"},{"pid":"4afe42611929dcefbad405466d72861dd585e9e6","tid":1076877,"uid":1014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:30:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">東華三院話咩事都冇呀</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01a6f6bc71076d670b263a64086505c2cb0e777","tid":1076877,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:31:34.000Z","msg":"監警會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21952922e5